                  </hi>. I am a cut glass manufacturer, in Falcon-square. On the evening of the 28th of March I was passing down Newgate-street, and felt somebody pulling at my pocket—I turned round and put my hand on the prisoner's collar—he was close to me, and shuffling my handkerchief from his left hand to his right—he threw it down—I took it up, and gate him in charge of an officer.</p>
